game.name: Stars  Royals BFF Party Night
game.description:
Almost everyone knows that Selena and Cinderella are widely known for their best friendship. They generally engage in organizing party in the club. Despite of coming from two different worlds, they love spending time together. Today they also made a similar plan. Yes, both are again attending a party together. Although these girls look very happy, they seem to be helpful while deciding the outfits for the party. Join Stars Royals BFF Party Night and be prepared to guide them to pick up the brightest and chick outfits for the party!
Remember one is royal princess and the other one comes from the celebrity world. Browse through their wardrobe and choose the outfits that are perfect to dance all night long in this one HTML5 dressing game! Apart from guiding them to pick up the nice dresses, make sure to prepare glitter, shine and confetti for the biggest party of their life. Begin the fun with Selena and dress her up with a pink color make-up with some highlight on her cheeks! 
A black leather dress with a zipper and some glamorous curls combined with a matching pair of blue platform shoes with pink ribbons will be perfect for her. Do not forget to complete her look with a pair of long black tassel earrings and a sparkling clutch. Smoky eyes and a classic red lipstick will suit the personality for Cinderella. Dress her up with a golden mini skirt, a green silk blouse and pair it with a golden clutch, a pearl necklace and a pair of red color classic shoes! Good luck to have the best time online with your friends in our more popular titles from the category of dress up games, no download required!
